      SuggestAddrInfo DrivingRouteResult.getSuggestAddrInfo()
      获取路线建议搜索信息 当SearchResult.error值为ERRORNO#AMBIGUOUS_ROURE_ADDR时，建议信息不为空
      SuggestAddrInfo TransitRouteResult.getSuggestAddrInfo()
      当SearchResult.error 为 SearchResult.ERRORNO#AMBIGUOUS_ROURE_ADDR 时 可通过此接口获取建议信息
      SuggestAddrInfo WalkingRouteResult.getSuggestAddrInfo()
      error 为 SearchResult.ERRORNO.AMBIGUOUS_ROURE_ADDR 时 可通过此接口获取建议信息
